      <p>Generator: 500 kVA (RM95,000)</p>

      <h3>Annual Outage Prevention</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Outages per year: 4 - 6</li>
        <li>Average outage duration: 3 hours</li>
        <li>Inventory loss prevented: RM120,000 - RM900,000</li>
